data.description: Welcome to this stunning home in the desirable  Boca Raton's Ironwedge community. The open concept floor plan includes a 2-story living space with a marble fireplace & a spacious open kitchen with marble countertops. Upstairs feature a private balcony in the primary suite & his and her closets along with a bathroom adorned in marble. With great schools, restaurants, major highways, Boca mall ETC nearby, this home offers luxury and convenience. Schedule a showing today to experience the beauty and elegance of this Boca Raton home!
